{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Web Workers API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Auf das&nbsp;<strong><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code></strong> Objekt (Der globale Scope des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a>) kann durch das Schlüsselwort <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/self\"><code>self</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zugegriffen werden. Einzelne weitere globale Funktionen, namespace&nbsp;Objekte und Konstruktoren, die nicht typischerweise mit dem Scope des Workers in Verbindung stehen, jedoch darauf verfügbar sind, können in der&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference\">JavaScript Reference</a>&nbsp;gefunden werden. Siehe auch:&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Functions_and_classes_available_to_workers\">Functions available to workers</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Dieses&nbsp;Interface erbt seine Eigenschaften aus dem Interface&nbsp;<em><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und seinem übergeordneten Interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Deshalbt implementiert es die Eigenschaften <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>, und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a>.</em></em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"dedicatedworkerglobalscope.name_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/name\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Der dem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a> (optional) gegebene Name, als er im Konstruktor&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/Worker\"><code>Worker()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> erzeugt wurde. Hauptsächlich nützlich für Debuggin.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"von_workerglobal_scope_geerbte_eigenschaften","title":"Von WorkerGlobal Scope geerbte Eigenschaften","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.self_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/self\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.self</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt eine Objektreferenz auf das&nbsp;<code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code> Objekt selbst zurück.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.console_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Gibt das mit dem Worker verbundene <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a> Objekt zurück.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.location_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/location\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Gibt das mit dem Worker verbundene <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Objekt zurück. Bei <code>WorkerLocation</code>&nbsp;handelt es sich um ein spezifisches location Objekt, welches aus Teilen des&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Objekts des Browserscope&nbsp;besteht,&nbsp; jedoch für den Worker angepasst wurde.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.navigator_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/navigator\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.navigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Git das mit dem Worker verbundene&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Objekt&nbsp; zurück. Bei&nbsp;<code>WorkerNavigator </code>handelt es sich um ein spezifisches navigations Objekt, welches aus Teilen des&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> Objekts des Browserscope besteht, jedoch für den Worker angepasst wurde.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.performance_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.performance</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Git das mit dem Worker verbunde&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a> Objekt zurück. Dabei handelt es sich um ein reguläres performance Objekt,&nbsp; welches jedoch nur teile der Eigenschaften und Methoden umfasst.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eventhandler","title":"Eventhandler","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>Dieses Interface erbt seine Eventhandler&nbsp; aus dem Interface {domxref(\"WorkerGlobalScope\")}} und seinen übergeordneten Interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Deshalb sind Eventhandler <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>, und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a> implementiert.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"dedicatedworkerglobalscope.onmessage_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/message_event\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.onmessage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Der entsprechende Code eines <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> der beim Aufruf des Events <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> aufgerufen wird. Diese Events sind vom Typ&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a> und werden aufgerufen, wenn der Worker eine Nachricht aus dem Dokument erhält, welcher Ihn gestartet hat (Beispiel:&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Worker/postMessage\"><code>Worker.postMessage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Methode.)&nbsp;</dd>\n <dt id=\"dedicatedworkerglobalscope.onmessageerror_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/messageerror_event\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.onmessageerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Der entsprechende Code eines <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> der beim Aufruf des Events <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/messageerror\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">messageerror</a></code> aufgerufen wird.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Dieses Interface erbt seine Methoden aus dem Interface <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und seinen übergordneten Interface&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Dementsprechend implementiert es Methoden von&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>WindowTimers</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowBase64</code></a>, und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"dedicatedworkerglobalscope.close_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/close\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Verwirft alle im&nbsp;<code>WorkerGlobalScope</code>'s Eventloop eingereihten Aufgaben und schließt den entsprechenden Scope.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dedicatedworkerglobalscope.postmessage_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/postMessage\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.postMessage()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sendet eine Nachricht — welche aus Javascript Objecten vom Typ&nbsp;<code>any</code>&nbsp;bestehen — zum übergeordneten Dokument, welches den Worker gestartet hat.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"geerbt_vom_workerglobalscope","title":"Geerbt vom WorkerGlobalScope","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.dump_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/dump\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.dump()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Gibt eine Nachricht in der Konsole aus.</dd>\n <dt id=\"workerglobalscope.importscripts_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/importScripts\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.importScripts()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Importiert ein oder mehrere Skripte in den Worker Scope. Es ist möglich beliebig viele, durch Kommas getrennt, zu spezifizieren. Beispiel:&nbsp;<code>importScripts('foo.js', 'bar.js');</code></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"aus_verschiedenen_orten_implementiert","title":"Aus verschiedenen Orten implementiert","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"windowbase64.atob_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/atob\"><code>WindowBase64.atob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Dekodiert einen String von Daten welcher mit base-64 codiert wurde.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowbase64.btoa\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/btoa\"><code>WindowBase64.btoa()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Erzeugt einen base-64 codierten ASCII String aus einem String von Binärdaten.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.clearinterval_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/clearInterval\"><code>WindowTimers.clearInterval()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Bricht die wiederholte Ausführung mit&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setInterval\"><code>WindowTimers.setInterval()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> ab.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.cleartimeout_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/clearTimeout\"><code>WindowTimers.clearTimeout()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Bricht die wiederholte Ausführung mit&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\"><code>WindowTimers.setTimeout()</code></a> ab.</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.setinterval_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/setInterval\"><code>WindowTimers.setInterval()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Plant die Ausführung einer Funktion alle X Millisekunden</dd>\n <dt id=\"windowtimers.settimeout\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/setTimeout\"><code>WindowTimers.setTimeout()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Setzt eine X Millisekunden Verzögerung für die Ausführung einer Funktion</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#dedicatedworkerglobalscope\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\">Using web workers</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Functions_and_classes_available_to_workers\">Functions available to workers</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Auf das DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope Objekt (Der globale Scope des Worker) kann durch das Schlüsselwort self (en-US) zugegriffen werden. Einzelne weitere globale Funktionen, namespace Objekte und Konstruktoren, die nicht typischerweise mit dem Scope des Workers in Verbindung stehen, jedoch darauf verfügbar sind, können in der JavaScript Reference gefunden werden. Siehe auch: Functions available to workers.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/dedicatedworkerglobalscope","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/dedicatedworkerglobalscope/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope","title":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope"}],"pageTitle":"DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}